title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displayed in data set dialog
description: The output parameter is not appearing as expected in the data set dialog while on the query result page.
OB: While in the query result page, no data is returned. The actual result is that the output parameter is not displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: Expect the output parameter to be visible and displayed in the edit data set dialog when on the query result page.
SR:
1. Navigate to the query result page.
2. Observe that no data is returned.
3. Check the edit data set dialog to confirm that the output parameter is not displayed.
